# 🇺🇸 The Art of the Dodge

**The Art of the Dodge** is a fast-paced browser game where you play as Donald Trump, dodging political pitfalls and collecting dollars on your quest to _Make America Great Again_. Can you collect all four MAGA caps and survive the chaos?

A high-stakes moments from The Art of the Dodge game:

