### Game Win

![Start screen](./assets/Game-3.png)

## 🎮 How to Play

**OBJECTIVE**  
Collect as many 💵 **dollars** as possible while trying to **Make America Great Again** by collecting four **MAGA caps**.

**AVOID**  
🚫 Joe Biden Head
🚫 Hillary Clinton Head
🚫 Mexican Taco Man
🚫 Fake News

Each of these will cost you lives, so stay sharp!

**CONTROLS**  
Use the **←** and **→** arrow keys to move Trump left and right.

**TIP**  
Good luck — **Trump is counting on you!**

